  "title": "Robata Grilled Dutch Jalapeno Bowl",
  "description": "A charred and snappy Dutch dish featuring jalapeno, robata-grilled to perfection, served in an earthenware bowl, perfect for a brunch mood. This shojin-friendly recipe is a unique blend of flavors and textures.",
