  "instructions": [
    "Preheat the robata grill to 400 degrees Fahrenheit.",
    "Grill the sliced jalapeno peppers for 2 minutes on each side, until charred.",
    "In a small bowl, mix together the robata grill sauce and olive oil.",
    "Brush the mixture onto the grilled jalapeno peppers.",
    "In the earthenware bowl, combine the mixed greens, cherry tomatoes, and red onion.",
    "Top the salad with the grilled jalapeno peppers and shredded Dutch cheese.",
    "Serve immediately and enjoy.",
    "Garnish with additional cherry tomatoes and red onion if desired."
